#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>csv import wizard: banking</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For most fields, you just need to use the dropdown to select the appropriate "
