#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Finish"
msgstr "CSV importimise nõustaja: lõpetamine"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:655
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "On reaching the Final page, the plugin automatically validates the "
#| "values. If the numeric value column/s is/are highlighted in green, then "
#| "the validation was successful and all that is necessary is to click "
#| "<guilabel>Import CSV</guilabel> and control then passes to the main "
#| "&kappname; program. However, if the start and/or end lines are "
#| "incorrectly set, or if the wrong columns were selected, the highlighting "
#| "will be in red, and an error message will appear indicating where the "
#| "error lies. The user will then need to click <guilabel>Back</guilabel> to "
#| "get to the relevant page to correct the error."
msgid ""
"On reaching the Final page, the plugin automatically validates the values. "
"If the numeric value column/s is/are highlighted in green, then the "
"validation was successful and all that is necessary is to click "
"<guibutton>Import CSV</guibutton> and control then passes to the main "
"&kmymoney; program. However, if the start and/or end lines are incorrectly "
"set, or if the wrong columns were selected, the highlighting will be in red, "
"and an error message will appear indicating where the error lies. The user "
"will then need to click <guibutton>Back</guibutton> to get to the relevant "
"page to correct the error."
msgstr ""
"Lõpetamise leheküljele jõudes kontrollib plugin automaatselt kõiki väärtusi. "
"Kui arvuliste väärtuste veerud on tähistatud rohelisega, oli kontroll edukas "
"ning vaja on veel vaid klõpsata nupule <guilabel>Impordi CSV</guilabel>, et "
"jõuaksid tagasi &kappname; peaaknasse. Kui aga algus- või lõpprida on "
"valesti määratud või valitud on väärad veerud, on esiletõstmise värviks "
"punane ning veateade osutab sellele, kus viga täpselt esineb. Kasutaja peab "
"seejärel klõpsama <guilabel>Tagasi</guilabel>, et jõuda lehele, kus viga "
"parandada."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:666
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "It might also be that if debit and credit columns are in use, one of "
#| "those columns may legitimately contain no entries. This would mean that "
#| "that column has no decimal symbol present, and this would result in a "
#| "warning. If you see that this is the case, you may click either of the "
#| "<guilabel>Accept</guilabel> buttons (<guilabel>Accept this</guilabel> or "
#| "<guilabel>Accept all</guilabel>.)"
msgid ""
"It might also be that if debit and credit columns are in use, one of those "
"columns may legitimately contain no entries. This would mean that that "
"column has no decimal symbol present, and this would result in a warning. If "
"you see that this is the case, you may click either of the buttons to accept "
"(<guibutton>Accept this</guibutton> or <guibutton>Accept all</guibutton>.)"
msgstr ""
"Samuti võib juhtuda, et kui kasutusel on deebeti- ja kreeditiveerud, siis "
"üks neist võib täiesti õigustatult kirjeid üldse mitte sisaldada. See "
"tähendab, et veerul puudub kümnendkoha eraldaja, mis toob kaasa hoiatuse. "
"Kui nii peaks juhtuma, võib klõpsata mõnele <guilabel>nõustumise</guilabel> "
"nupule (<guilabel>Nõus sellega</guilabel> või <guilabel>Nõus kõigiga</"
"guilabel>)."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid "Decimal Symbol"
msgstr "Kümnendkoha eraldaja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:675
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another possible problem might be that the selected decimal symbol is "
"incorrect. Selecting the symbol to match the data should clear that error. "
"Normally, you should not need to change this selection. Note that the "
"<guilabel>Decimal Symbol</guilabel> must be set to match your file, not your "
"locale. If your locale setting has a different value, conversion will be "
"seen to take place. The display of the file in the upper part of the window "
"will show numeric fields highlighted in green if the current setting "
"produces valid results, otherwise in red. The highlighting also reflects the "
"<guilabel>Start line</guilabel> and <guilabel>End line</guilabel> settings. "
"There could be warnings if any of the selected cells appear not to contain "
"the selected symbol."
msgstr ""
"Probleeme võib tekitada ka see, kui valitud kümnendkoha eraldaja on väär. "
"Andmetega sobiva eraldaja valimine peaks selle tõrke kõrvaldama. Tavaliselt "
"ei ole seda valikut põhjust muuta. Pane tähele, et <guilabel>kümnendkoha "
"eraldaja</guilabel> peab kokku sobima sinu faili, mitte sinu lokaadiga. Kui "
"lokaadis on teistsugune eraldaja, siis võetakse ette teisendus. Faili kuva "
"akna ülaosas näitab arvuvälju roheliselt, kui kehtiv valik annab korrektse "
"tulemuse, või punaselt, kui see nii ei ole. See esiletõstmine puudutab ka "
"<guilabel>algusrea</guilabel> ja <guilabel>lõpprea</guilabel> valikuid. Kui "
"mõni valitud lahtritest ei sisalda valitud sümbolit, ongi tulemuseks hoiatus."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thousands Symbol"
msgstr "Tuhandete eraldaja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This does not need to be selected, as it is set automatically based on the "
"<guilabel>Decimal Symbol</guilabel>. It is provided purely as a guide. In "
"addition, the selector will be inactive if none of the values to be imported "
"is greater or equal to 1000."
msgstr ""
"Seda pole vaja määrata, sest see kehtestatakse automaatselt "
"<guilabel>kümnendkoha eraldaja</guilabel> põhjal. Siin on see põhiliselt "
"lihtsalt teadmiseks. Lisaks pole valik üldse kasutatavgi, kui ükski "
"imporditavatest väärtustest ei ole suurem kui 1000."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:699
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import CSV"
msgstr "Impordi CSV"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:700
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Clicking this button tells the plugin to actually import the data from "
#| "the file, based on the choices you have made above. &kappname; will "
#| "prompt you for the correct account into which to import the data."
msgid ""
"Clicking this button tells the plugin to actually import the data from the "
"file, based on the choices you have made above. &kmymoney; will prompt you "
"for the correct account into which to import the data."
msgstr ""
"Sellele nupule klõpsates antakse pluginale korraldus tegelikult importida "
"andmed failist vastavalt valikutele, mida oled eelnevalt langetanud. "
"&kappname; pärib sinu käest kontot, millesse andmed importida."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid "Make QIF File"
msgstr "Loo QIF-fail"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:709
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This button gives you the ability, after the import has been completed, "
#| "to save the data from the csv file as a qif file, should you require one "
#| "for any reason. This was actually the original functionality that drove "
#| "the creation of this plugin. However, as &kappname; itself is now able to "
#| "export a qif file, the capability is now probably of little use and is "
#| "likely to be removed eventually."
msgid ""
"This button gives you the ability, after the import has been completed, to "
"save the data from the CSV file as a QIF file, should you require one for "
"any reason. This was actually the original functionality that drove the "
"creation of this plugin. However, as &kmymoney; itself is now able to export "
"a qif file, the capability is now probably of little use and is likely to be "
"removed eventually."
msgstr ""
"See nupp annab võimaluse pärast impordi lõpetamist salvestada CSV-faili "
"andmed QIF-failina, kui see peaks mingil põhjusel vajalik olema. Õigupoolest "
"selle võimaluse pakkumine algselt innustaski pluginat looma. Aga et nüüd "
"suudab &kappname; ka ise QIF-faili eksportida, on selle tähtsus tõsiselt "
"vähenenud ning arvatavasti see võimalus millalgi üldse kaob."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finishing up"
msgstr "Lõpetamine"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:720
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For a <guilabel>Banking</guilabel> import, the plugin has finished, and "
#| "&kappname; will prompt you, as stated above, for the correct account into "
#| "which to import the data. For an <guilabel>Investment</guilabel> import, "
#| "however, a little more may be required. If, during import of a "
#| "transaction, the plugin finds no valid transaction type, it will display "
#| "the offending transaction, and the user may select a valid type to "
#| "substitute, depending on the combination of quantity, price, and amount "
#| "values. For every transaction, the plugin will validate the column "
#| "contents to ensure they match the action type. For instance, if a "
#| "quantity appears but no price or amount, it is assumed that the "
#| "transaction can be only an Add or Remove Shares. Or, if there is an "
#| "amount but no quantity or price, then a Dividend is assumed, etc.."
msgid ""
"For a <guilabel>Banking</guilabel> import, the plugin has finished, and "
"&kmymoney; will prompt you, as stated above, for the correct account into "
"which to import the data. For an <guilabel>Investment</guilabel> import, "
"however, a little more may be required. If, during import of a transaction, "
"the plugin finds no valid transaction type, it will display the offending "
"transaction, and the user may select a valid type to substitute, depending "
"on the combination of quantity, price, and amount values. For every "
"transaction, the plugin will validate the column contents to ensure they "
"match the action type. For instance, if a quantity appears but no price or "
"amount, it is assumed that the transaction can be only an Add or Remove "
"Shares. Or, if there is an amount but no quantity or price, then a Dividend "
"is assumed, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pangatehingute</guilabel> importimise korral on plugin oma töö "
"lõpetanud ning &kappname; pärib, nagu eespool mainitud, sinu käest konto "
"nime, kuhu andmed importida. <guilabel>Investeeringu</guilabel> importimise "
"korral on aga üht-teist veel vaja. Kui plugin ei leia tehingu importimisel "
"kehtivat tehingutüüpi, näidatakse vigast tehingut ja kasutaja saab valida "
"sõltuvalt koguse ja hinna kombinatsioonist sellele sobiva tüübi. Iga tehingu "
"korral kontrollib plugin veeru sisu, et see ikka vastaks tehingu tüübile. "
"Kui näiteks on olemas kvantiteet, mitte aga hinda või kogust, siis "
"eeldatakse, et tehing saab olla ainult aktsiate lisamine või eemaldamine. "
"Kui aga on ainult kogus, mitte aga kvantiteeti või hinda, siis eeldatakse "
"dividendi jne."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:734
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you wish to save your settings, remember to click the "
